I67T1``SEC. 2. AMERICAN VIETNAM WAR POW/MIA ASYLUM PROGRAM.

S5800

I21``(a) T4Asylum for Eligible AliensK._Notwithstanding any other provision of law, the Attorney General shall grant refugee status in the United States to any alien described in subsection (b), upon the application of that alien.

