I16(III) A violent attack upon an internationally protected person (as defined in section 1116(b)(4) of title 18) or upon the liberty of such a person.

I16(IV) An assassination.

I16(V) The use of any_

S5804

I34(a) biological agent, chemical agent, or nuclear weapon or device, or

I34(b) explosive, firearm, or other weapon or dangerous device (other than for mere personal monetary gain),

