S5800

I56with intent to endanger, directly or indirectly, the safety of one or more individuals or to cause substantial damage to property.

I16(VI) A threat, attempt, or conspiracy to do any of the foregoing.

I77(iv) ``Engage in terrorist activity'' defined

I14As used in this chapter, the term ``engage in terrorist activity'' means, in an individual capacity or as a member of an organization_

I16(I) to commit or to incite to commit, under circumstances indicating an intention to cause death or serious bodily injury, a terrorist activity;

I16(II) to prepare or plan a terrorist activity;

I16(III) to gather information on potential targets for terrorist activity;

I16(IV) to solicit funds or other things of value for_

