I34(aa) a terrorist activity;

I34(bb) a terrorist organization described in clause (vi)(I) or (vi)(II); or

I34(cc) a terrorist organization described in clause (vi)(III), unless the solicitor can demonstrate by clear and convincing evidence that he did not know, and should not reasonably have known, that the organization was a terrorist organization;

