I79(2) Costs of removal to port of removal for aliens admitted or permitted to land

I12In the case of an alien who has been admitted or permitted to land and is ordered removed, the cost (if any) of removal of the alien to the port of removal shall be at the expense of the appropriation for the enforcement of this chapter.

